headline: Anne Wojcicki's bid to buy back 23andMe may not end legal fight over DNA customer data
summary: Anne Wojcicki's winning bid to reclaim control of 23andMe doesn't necessarily end the fight over what happens to the DNA of 15 million people collected by the bankrupt consumer genomics company.
